<div style="font-family:serif;">
:<font size="15">בּנימין</font></div>

===Pronunciation===
בּנימין / binyâmîyn / bin-yaw-mene'

===Etymology===
From [[בּן]] {{HH|1121}} and [[ימין]] {{HH|3225}}; son of (the) right hand; Binjamin, youngest son of Jacob; also the tribe descended from him, and its territory

===Proper noun===
'''בּנימין'''

# [[Benjamin]].

